Explanation:
The Endpoint getPrintShopStatistics is annotated with @RequestMapping(value = "/printshops/stats", method = RequestMethod.GET) and secured with ROLE_MANAGER. This means the endpoint is accessible only via GET requests to /printshops/stats (relative to the application context, and with no path parameters in this path). Since there are no mappings for other HTTP methods on this path, only GET is supported according to the code. We did not see any class-level prefix that would alter the path, so the full path remains /printshops/stats. HEAD/OPTIONS/TRACE/PUT/POST/PATCH are not defined here, so they are not supported by this code as written.
